<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white p-3 md:p-6"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    <!-- Esercizio 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
    <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-2xl border-3 border-yellow-400">
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <%= imparare_tutti_badge(1) %>
        Nell'istogramma sono rappresentati i dati relativi alla lingua straniera preferita dai ragazzi di 14 anni. Osserva e rispondi alle domande.
      </p>

      <div class="mb-4">
        <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p259/p259_01.jpg", class: "max-w-full h-auto mx-auto", alt: "Istogramma lingue straniere" %>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-cyan-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Quanti ragazzi sono stati intervistati?</span>
          <input type="text" data-correct-answer="200" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent">
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-cyan-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Quanti preferiscono l'inglese?</span>
          <input type="text" data-correct-answer="80" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent">
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-cyan-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Quanti preferiscono il francese?</span>
          <input type="text" data-correct-answer="30" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent">
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-cyan-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Quanti preferiscono il tedesco?</span>
          <input type="text" data-correct-answer="20" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent">
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-cyan-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Quanti preferiscono lo spagnolo?</span>
          <input type="text" data-correct-answer="70" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Esercizio 2 -->
    <div>
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <%= numero_esercizio_badge(2) %>
        Rappresenta nell'ideogramma la quantità annua di pioggia caduta nelle città registrate in tabella. Segui l'esempio.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">1 <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p259/output-1715938802259_826_500_47_43.png", class: "inline-block w-8 h-auto align-middle", alt: "Simbolo pioggia" %> = 100 mm</p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2">Dati raccolti</p>
          <table class="w-full border-collapse border border-cyan-400">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 bg-custom-blue-light text-center text-gray-800">Città</th>
                <th class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 bg-custom-blue-light text-center text-gray-800">Pioggia (mm)</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">Torino</td>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">800</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">Como</td>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">1 000</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">La Spezia</td>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">600</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2">Ideogramma</p>
          <table class="w-full border-collapse border border-cyan-400">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 bg-custom-blue-light text-center text-gray-800">Città</th>
                <th class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 bg-custom-blue-light text-center text-gray-800">Pioggia (mm)</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white font-bold">Torino</td>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">
                  <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p259/output-1715938802259_573_578_322_39.png", class: "max-w-full h-auto", alt: "8 simboli pioggia" %>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">Como</td>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white h-12">
                  <!-- Disegna 10 simboli pioggia -->
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">La Spezia</td>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white h-12">
                  <!-- Disegna 6 simboli pioggia -->
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Esercizio 3 -->
    <div>
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <%= numero_esercizio_badge(3) %>
        Nella tabella sono riportate le temperature medie registrate in una città del centro Italia in un anno intero. Rappresenta con un diagramma cartesiano.
      </p>

      <div class="text-center">
        <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p259/p259_02.jpg", class: "max-w-full h-auto mx-auto", alt: "Tabella temperature e diagramma cartesiano" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
  </div>
</div>
